    "In this period Sandrart composed his <em>magnum opus</em>, the <em>L'Academia Todesca della Architectura Scultura et Pictura, oder Teutsche Academie der Edlen Bau-, Bild- und Mahlerey- K\u00fcnste</em>, published in Nuremberg in 1675.": [
