    "He also published an illustrated study on ancient gods, <em>Iconologia deorum</em> that year.": [],
    "A treatise on Roman topography, <em>Romae antiquae et novae theatrum</em> appeared in 1684.": [],
    "But it is the <em>Teutsche Academie</em> that gained him most fame.": [],
    "The work was in its turn used as one of the main sources for <em>De Groote Schouburgh der Nederlantsche Konstschilders en Schilderessen</em> by <a href=\"/houbrakena\">Arnold Houbraken</a>, published in 1718-1721 and remains an important primary source today.": [],
